---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title={`Terms of Service | ${SITE.name}`} description="Terms of Service for VettedPick.com">
  <div class="article-prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: July 1, 2026</em></p>

    <p>
      By accessing {SITE.url}, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do
      not use this website.
    </p>

    <h2>Use of the Site</h2>
    <p>
      {SITE.name} provides product reviews, comparisons, and affiliate links for informational
      purposes. Content is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied.
    </p>

    <h2>No Professional Advice</h2>
    <p>
      Our reviews and recommendations are editorial opinions based on research and publicly available
      information. They do not constitute professional, financial, or legal advice.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Relationships</h2>
    <p>
      We earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through Amazon affiliate links on this
      site. This does not increase the price you pay. See our footer for full Amazon Associates and
      FTC disclosures.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy of Information</h2>
    <p>
      Product prices, availability, and specifications change frequently. We strive for accuracy but
      cannot guarantee that all information is current at the time you read it. Always verify details
      on Amazon before purchasing.
    </p>

    <h2>External Links</h2>
    <p>
      Our site contains links to third-party websites including Amazon.com. We are not responsible for
      the content, policies, or practices of external sites.
    </p>

    <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>
      All original content on {SITE.name} is owned by us unless otherwise noted. Product names and
      trademarks belong to their respective owners and are used for identification and comparison
      purposes only.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the fullest extent permitted by law, {SITE.name} shall not be liable for any damages arising
      from your use of this site or purchase of products through our affiliate links.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes
      constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions? Contact us at <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
